                <img src="/upload/KD/Ingressbilder/Forskningsbilder/Kavli-prize_100.gif" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/kd/press-contacts/Press-releases/2010/Kavli-Prizes-to-eight-scientists.html?id=607215" title="">
                        Kavli Prizes to eight scientists
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Education and Research, 03.06.2010]</p>
                <p>The names of the  2010 Kavli Prize Laureates was announced by the President of the Norwegian Academy of Science and Letters, Nils Christian Stenseth, on June 3 in Oslo, Norway.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
