            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/kd/press-contacts/Press-releases/2010/agreements-on-cooperation-in-higher-educ.html?id=601959" title="">
                        Agreements on cooperation with Russia
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Education and Research, 27.04.2010]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Ministry of Education and Research and representatives of the Russian Federation has signed agreements on cooperation in higher education and meteorology.</p>
                
                
